 />\n<br />\n最勁我覺得係放大電筒<br />\n買粒鑽石放大之類<br />\n要發達唔難<br />\n<br />\n要偷任何野可以用縮小<br />\n<br />\n放大自己條撚得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n憨鳩 <br />\n如果電話亭 <br />\n如果我有幾千億美金<br />\n如果我有條大撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌打你啦</blockquote><br />\n我敢如果電話亭一定係最屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd510d9b163d1316f1490471f23ae3618e4d4b2f","tid":129912,"uid":57357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T12:26:42.000Z","msg":"太耐無睇，呢排玩番多啦A夢大富翁，有D法寶好似完全唔撚知係咩黎咁<br />\n<br />\n處境調換槍都幾好用吖其實"},{"pid":"315b20ad7cb46abb0ecf01faa82654e73513075c","tid":129912,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T12:43:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果電話亭唔夠方便仲有好多不隨機性<br />\n<br />\n最勁我覺得係放大電筒<br />\n買粒鑽石放大之類<br />\n要發達唔難<br />\n<br />\n要偷任何野可以用縮小<br />\n<br />\n放大自己條撚得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n憨鳩 <br />\n如果電話亭 <br />\n如果我有幾千億美金<br />\n如果我有條大撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌打你啦</blockquote><br />\n我敢如果電話亭一定係最屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本有一大班小學雞憨鳩仔連叮噹都未睇過就係到話人唔明唔識未睇過<br />\n點知自己先係衝出嚟柒"},{"pid":"c737b0158ffbe9f7bd9bc9d57eb395aef3b5c3cf","tid":129912,"uid":26931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"時光機啦梗係"},{"pid":"e1cd779d13788fe1d3421019e3e120ef46752d93","tid":129912,"uid":41589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解大人唔要時光機要隨意門？用黎返工？</blockquote><br />\n用黎旅行都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以我覺得樓上第一樣就諗住用黎返工𠴱幾件先係奴性重，正常人一諗就緊係拎黎旅行週圍去啦，唔明呢幾位點解要衝出黎柒。</blockquote><br />\n有錢咪去到旅行囉，我有時光機中次六合彩，我洗要隨意門旅行？</blockquote><br />\n有錢都要坐飛機。都有機會出事 加埋你飛usa 都要十幾粒鐘。隨意門零危機零時間"},{"pid":"518d0b171c88d291e4ee4784c14fd990f742ebe5","tid":129912,"uid":84015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:27:21.000Z","msg":"預言日記最屈機"},{"pid":"ca26f1bd0ed31f607f68d3ff5eb75dedb5462226","tid":129912,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:49:29.000Z","msg":"隱身斗蓬"},{"pid":"a7ec0971347f5a59134d09c83c355dc48c6f85aa","tid":129912,"uid":20563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"之前有一集話有個法寶將d 野變成熱潮<br />\n令樣野價錢提高<br />\n大雄就係度炒汽水蓋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港地有呢樣就人人發達去炒<br />\n仲洗隨意門返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b496b40274b4c38271e59b3ba677002dcdefbdc5","tid":129912,"uid":61889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:06:19.000Z","msg":"如果電話亭太唔方便，下下要對住個電話講，謊言800同弄假成真器要講反話一樣好唔方便，相反食完夢想成真藥片只要諗一諗就所有願望都可以成真，方便好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04bb5c2c56383f3202f6b94c67b0210f1f86cc84","tid":129912,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:07:15.000Z","msg":"走一轉軍火就賺大錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e030e30d3781e335700325779394aa7c76c0e1","tid":129912,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T14:11:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果電話亭太唔方便，下下要對住個電話講，謊言800同弄假成真器要講反話一樣好唔方便，相反食完夢想成真藥片只要諗一諗就所有願望都可以成真，方便好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一諗就出嚟都幾危險<br />\n唔可以亂諗野"},{"pid":"a301f4fc7